{"type": "article", "id": 27554, "title": "自行车专用雨伞", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-31T07:01:46Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 92, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702134107nDqTkJCmdOMXbZAB.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>          </p>\n<p>即使是下雨天也可以舒舒服服地骑着自行车出行——LEAFXPRO 团队的设计师们以此为理念设计出了一款专门为自行车设计的雨伞，这一次他们带来了产品的升级版。LEAFXPRO 2 的造型根据空气动力学研发，能够在恶劣的天气情况下能保证骑行的顺畅，而且组装起来也非常简单。除了本体之外，LEAFXPRO 2 还提供了两款可选配件，一件是可以保护骑手身体两侧的防雨罩，另一件则专门为罩住后座儿童椅而设计，家长们也不用担心孩子会淋湿了。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.indiegogo.com/projects/leafxpro-2-bicycle-every-day--4#/\">链接</a>参与众筹，最低价为 49 美元。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021341033drxAkFwb6yoGIzq.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.3225\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021341047ZyQMrRuOJameV9S.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.2\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702134105DdqTezl6GXNIJs9j.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.692\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021341060veO2hdVn41bRNk7.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61204013\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}